::SnowCat::

She looked back at the bushes for a second. "I don't think the one 
that is hiding will step out into the open." She turned back and 
looked at Ramulus. "Perhaps it would be best if we leave the shy one 
over there alone for now.  It has not come out to attack us.  I think 
it will leave once we depart. Shall we?"  She motioned with her head 
to leave.

> ::Ramulus::
> 
> Ramulus looks at SnowCat. "Nice to meet you," he says, "My name's 
Ramulus."
> 
> He looks her over. "You can get some food at the Ark, if its still 
intact. If 
> not, I can take you to base."
> 
> He was still keeping track of the other bot in the bushes, ready to 
react if 
> neccessary.
